---
title: Beef 'Larb' Salad Wraps with Green Rice and Toasted Peanuts
description: Larb' is a traditional Thai and Laotian ground meat salad. This version is quick to make and fun to eat. Assembling your own wrap encourages individuality, while still be able to enjoy all the classic flavours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/wraps-de-laitue-au-lap-de-boeuf-aec65d44.jpg
